A well-deserved tax break is another thing Canadians can look forward to starting this weekend!

The GST holiday starts today! 

There is no federal tax on 100s of items from now until February 15th. That includes things like:

🍎 prepared food and takeout;
🧸 diapers;
👚 kids clothing; 
🥾 kids winter boots and books;

and 100s more!

